title: Does blue Ez still trump Triforce rush Ez?
body:
I've been using this guide recently for the triforce rush Ez and it works pretty decently, but everyone keeps asking me why I'm not going blue Ez. Is it still good with the changes to Muramana?

Here is the guide: http://lol.inven.co.kr/dataninfo/champion/manualToolView.php?idx=122602
